02:39:10.093 --> 02:39:11.261
Tilda ?

1665
02:39:14.097 --> 02:39:15.473
Ada apa ?

1666
02:39:15.474 --> 02:39:17.935
Aku datang mau mengatakan
selamat tinggal.


1667
02:39:18.060 --> 02:39:20.562
Selamat tinggal ?
